println("  R(3,8) = 28 (perfect)            | Notable coincidence   | p~0.06 | 🟡")
println("  Two R(3,n) = perfect             | Interesting pattern   | p~0.06 | 🟡")

println("")
println("OVERALL: Most tautological/trivial. R(3,3)=6, R(3,8)=28 coincidence mildly interesting.")
println("No deep structural connection — Small Number effect likely.")
